General Assembly Of North Carolina Session 2025
1 Madison, McDowell, Mitchell, New Hanover, Onslow, Pamlico, Pender, Polk, Rowan,
2 Rutherford, Stanly, Stokes, Surry, Vance, Washington, and Yancey."
3 SECTION 7. This act becomes effective the first Monday in December of 2026, and
4 elections in 2026 shall be conducted accordingly.
